                            <comment id="13013982" author="tavoaqp" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2011 15:01:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Affects mahout-core and mahout-utils&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13013983" author="tavoaqp" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2011 15:04:23 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Sean, I created the patch (hope I did right). Regarding whether committing it as an optimization or not, Ted and Robert suggested to wait until having further results. The intention is to implement the full Elkan optimization which will modify almost entirely the current version of K-means.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13013990" author="srowen" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2011 15:18:52 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;OK, would it be better to consider this an open issue for later, to cover updating the K-means code? or would you rather get this in now as a prelude to that?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13013994" author="tavoaqp" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2011 15:47:32 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I prefer to get in this now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
